TITLE: Implementing 7702 Gas Estimator with Smart Account Client
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to create a Smart Account Client using the default7702GasEstimator along with other configurations for a modular account. The function creates a 7702-compatible smart account client with custom gas estimation.
