TITLE: Viewing Session Key Permissions
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to view all current permissions for a given session key using the view functions provided by the Session Key Plugin. It includes checks for access control, time range, and various spending limits.
SOURCE: https://github.com/alchemyplatform/aa-sdk/blob/main/docs/pages/smart-contracts/other-accounts/modular-account/session-keys/supported-permissions.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const sessionKeyPlugin = new SessionKeyPlugin()
const accountAddress = "0x..."
const sessionKeyAddress = "0x..."

// Get access control type
const accessControlType = await sessionKeyPlugin.readFromPlugin(
  "getAccessControlType",
  [accountAddress, sessionKeyAddress]
)

// Get time range
const [validAfter, validUntil] = await sessionKeyPlugin.readFromPlugin(
  "getKeyTimeRange",
  [accountAddress, sessionKeyAddress]
)

// Get native token spend limit
const nativeTokenSpendLimit = await sessionKeyPlugin.readFromPlugin(
  "getNativeTokenSpendLimitInfo",
  [accountAddress, sessionKeyAddress]
)

// Get gas spend limit
const [gasSpendLimit, shouldReset] = await sessionKeyPlugin.readFromPlugin(
  "getGasSpendLimit",
  [accountAddress, sessionKeyAddress]
)

// Get ERC20 spend limit (for a specific token)
const tokenAddress = "0x..."
const erc20SpendLimit = await sessionKeyPlugin.readFromPlugin(
  "getERC20SpendLimitInfo",
  [accountAddress, sessionKeyAddress, tokenAddress]
)

// Get required paymaster
const requiredPaymaster = await sessionKeyPlugin.readFromPlugin(
  "getRequiredPaymaster",
  [accountAddress, sessionKeyAddress]
)
```

