TITLE: Updating Fee Options with Multiplier in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This example demonstrates the transition from using Percent to Multiplier for fee options. It shows how to specify maxFeePerGas and maxPriorityFeePerGas using the new Multiplier type, which represents direct multiplication of the estimated value.
