TITLE: Middleware Execution Order List
DESCRIPTION: Ordered list of middleware components that run during Smart Account Client operations, including dummy paymaster data generation, fee estimation, gas estimation, custom middleware, paymaster data handling, and user operation simulation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/alchemyplatform/aa-sdk/blob/main/docs/pages/concepts/middleware.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: plain
CODE:
```
1. dummyPaymasterAndData - Generates a dummy paymaster and data for gas estimation if using a paymaster (default: noop)
2. feeEstimator - Estimates the fees for a user operation
3. gasEstimator - Estimates the gas limits for a user operation
4. customMiddleware - Allows you define custom middleware to run before requesting sponsorship
5. paymasterAndData - Requests a gas sponsorship from a paymaster
6. userOperationSimulator - Simulates a user operation to check if it will be successful
```

