TITLE: Handling Redirect Flow Authentication in React with Account Kit
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates how to handle authentication redirects when using the redirect flow in Account Kit. It uses the useSignerStatus hook to track the authentication state and display appropriate UI during the authentication process.
SOURCE: https://github.com/alchemyplatform/aa-sdk/blob/main/site/pages/react/login-methods/social-login.mdx#2025-04-22_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
import { useEffect } from "react";
import { useSignerStatus } from "@account-kit/react";

// Inside your component
const { isAuthenticating } = useSignerStatus();

// Show loading state during authentication
useEffect(() => {
  if (isAuthenticating) {
    // Show loading UI while authentication completes
  }
}, [isAuthenticating]);
```

