TITLE: MultiOwnerPlugin Core Functions in Solidity
DESCRIPTION: These are the core Solidity functions exposed by the MultiOwnerPlugin that allow account owners to update and read the current owners of a Modular Account. The updateOwners function allows adding and removing owners, while ownersOf returns all current owners of an account.
